        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">The provided European volume is an estimated value as described below. 

In 2020, vinyl acetate Global production amounted to 8.47 mtpa, according to &lt;https://www.globaldata.com/store/report/vinyl-acetate-monomer-market-analysis/&gt;, accessed on 2023-11-01.

The European counterpart is estimated to be 1.53 mtpa, considering the nominal GDP of EU in 2020, equal to 15'370'461'303'996 US$ and in the World, equal to                                     85'215'150'558'552 US$, available here: &lt;https://api.worldbank.org/v2/en/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD?downloadformat=excel&gt; , accessed on 2023-11-01.


</productionVolumeComment>
